<p>Hi, I'm willing to join the Junior Staff team.</p>
<p>1. I wish to be able to contribute more to the site itself, and help other people post a good SCP on the site, so that they can feel valued as a member of the site. It's also a good experience for me to develop my analysing skills, and allow me to know more about other people's and my own hidden literary talents.</p>
